{"tid":1479452,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"用817紅土遊行黎宣傳818民陣2pm維園集會","createTime":"2019-08-17T02:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T02:31:11.000Z","uid":231583,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"882c15edff7dfb8524f55d31decd3db0e9b19139","tid":1479452,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:10:18.000Z","msg":"我諗好多人都認同817, 818都需要和平比子彈外國做野，狗無啦啦last min先批817遊行分分鐘係為左搞事打擊818出席人數<br />\n<br />\n人多就唔怕鬼，而且有鬼就用索帶捉住佢係佢面上寫平反六四再影佢高清合照，絕對和平理性非暴力<br />\n<br />\n817會有成堆記者影住遊行人士，如果可以禮貌地用唔同方式例如標語、口號、banner宣傳818大遊行，和平結束後就慢慢散去，唔做任何令狗有藉口清場行動，記者其實係幫緊我地做緊818免費宣傳<br />\n<br />\n817 3:30pm 海心公園<br />\n818 2pm 民陣維園集會<br />\n要見到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重點：我地今日應該邊行邊宣傳818<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"52ebc78aa15b7feac076447c0f4362379c157aca","tid":1479452,"uid":146737,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:10:59.000Z","msg":"【突發文宣計劃！】「牆紙」！首個針對中立淺藍黃嘅大型文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n攬炒宣言.mp3<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sendspace.com/file/0pn4yv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sendspace.com%2Ffile%2F0pn4yv&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75UcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=ffeb6a7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sendspace.com/file/0pn4yv</a><br />\n梁繼平宣言.mp3<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sendspace.com/file/jqtj8r\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sendspace.com%2Ffile%2Fjqtj8r&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75UcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=e500390a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sendspace.com/file/jqtj8r</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vu1TVgv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvu1TVgv.jpg&h=4114d504&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pi